===Prefixes===
* [[Hajji|Haji]], one who had made the [[Hajj|Muslim pilgrimage]] to [[Mecca]].
* [[Emir|Mir]], generally indicates [[sayid|seyed]] and/or royal descent.

===Suffixes===
*'''-i''', a common suffix used for surnames.
*'''-zai''', "descendant of" used commonly in Pashtun surnames.
*'''-nia''', "His/Her highness (Title)".
*'''-bakhsh''', "granted by".
*'''-dad''' ''(Middle Persian: Dāta)'', "given by".

